reviewText: This is the best children's music out there!
My daughter is almost six and has Down Syndrome.  She is captivated by the video and sings along with it all the time.  Well done and great price.

I highly recommend this DVD. The quality of the video and the production value is high, much more so than your average targeted-for-children productions. All the songs I believe are original songs, and most of them are pretty good. Also, the quality of the instruments played/recorded are close to "regular" album caliber as well, as is the variation of song genres. Many songs are filmed with children dancing along with the video, which our daughter really appreciates (she's memorized all the dance moves!). All in all, highly recommend this DVD. Perfect for an active toddler who likes to sing and dance along.

Our 14-month old son doesn't get to watch much TV, and what he does watch doesn't really hold his attention very well. Not so with the Mamas - he bounces along through the whole DVD (if we let him) and loves it.
The Swingset Mamas' original music is fun and educational! My girls love to sing and dance to the songs!
Dance Around the House This DVD is great for the whole family. My 4 boys ranging from 5 - 11 years old sing the Swingset Mama songs all day long!!!! What a find!
An excellent selection for the younger set. My nieces and nephews really enjoyed it. ENJOY!
My children LOVE this DVD.  I really enjoy this music also; and the skits are very clever and entertaining.  The world needs more Mamas music.
